title.en: Kazoku ni Yakudatazu to Iware Tsuzuketa Watashi ga, Mashou no Koushaku Kishi-sama no Saiai ni naru made

Konyaku Haki no Tsugi wa Gisou Konyaku. Sate, Sono Ji wa...
